  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6496b38e-9a7d-4afc-489a-94989ea94d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 246px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505095902\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6496b38e-9a7d-4afc-489a-94989ea94d00/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：编辑部 HXs</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Figure公司通过强化学习，成功实现机器人的自然步态。利用高效物理模拟器，仅用几小时完成相当于多年训练的数据，训练出的策略无需额外调整即可「零样本」迁移至真实机器人。</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在训练机器人，都不需要真实数据了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚刚，Figure提出了一种全新的基于RL的端到端网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">只需要在纯模拟环境中进行训练，用几个小时生成模拟数据，就能让Figure 02像人类一样自然行走了！</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/73ab2dd6-82a5-4d01-709c-6dfbb7b04d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-width=\"1085\" data-height=\"606\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505095907\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/73ab2dd6-82a5-4d01-709c-6dfbb7b04d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">该方法的亮点如下：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在模拟环境中运用强化学习，让机器人不断试错，学会像人类一样走路。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过高保真物理模拟器，仅用几个小时，就模拟出多年的数据。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">将模拟中的域随机化与机器人上的高频扭矩反馈相结合，无需微调，就能把模拟环境中的策略应用于真实机器人。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0bf1f058-cfc6-4ff8-d75e-e8b4984d0b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505095908\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0bf1f058-cfc6-4ff8-d75e-e8b4984d0b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">更让人惊喜的是，一个神经网络策略就能控制一大批机器人！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过一个高保真物理模拟器，Figure最新的机器人仅用几个小时，就能模拟出几年的数据。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/656b2c32-2c39-444a-c170-0e59e94f2000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505095909\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/656b2c32-2c39-444a-c170-0e59e94f2000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了把模拟环境的训练成果应用到真实机器人上，团队采用了两种办法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一是在模拟训练时进行域随机化，让机器人接触不同的物理属性；二是在真实机器人上安装高频扭矩反馈装置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样一来，模拟环境中训练好的策略，无需任何微调，就可以「零样本」迁移到真实硬件上。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12389b7e-552e-49f9-fa30-c15874509e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505095910\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12389b7e-552e-49f9-fa30-c15874509e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在强化学习中，控制器通过不断试错，根据奖励信号来调整自己的行为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Figure在高保真模拟环境中训练RL控制器，运行数千个具有不同参数和场景的虚拟人形机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种多样化的训练，使训练出的策略能直接用在真实的Figure 02机器人上，走出稳健的人类步伐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Figure基于RL的训练方法，大大缩短了开发时间，在现实世界中表现也很稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span leaf=\"\">强化学习训练</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">用强化学习方法，在GPU加速的物理模拟环境中，训练行走控制器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个模拟环境效率超高，短短几个小时就能收集到相当于数年的模拟训练数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在模拟器中，数千个Figure 02机器人并行训练，每个机器人的物理参数都不一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它们会遇到各种各样的情况，像不同的地形，执行器动力学变化，以及被绊倒、滑倒和推搡等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时，一个神经网络策略学习控制所有的机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63703895-8ca1-4431-0acf-268d669bcc00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.49212233549582945\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"277\" data-imgfileid=\"505095911\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63703895-8ca1-4431-0acf-268d669bcc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">人形机器人有个很大的优势，它的硬件平台通用性很强，能执行类似人类的任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，RL训练出来的策略，有时不是最佳的，没办法让机器人走出人类走路的感觉，比如脚跟先着地、脚尖蹬地，手臂摆动和腿部动作的配合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，在训练时，会奖励那些走路轨迹像人的机器人，把偏好融入学习中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些轨迹为策略允许生成的行走风格建立了先验条件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了走路轨迹像人，研究者还设置了其他奖励条件，比如优化机器人速度跟踪、功耗更低，更好地应对外界干扰和地形变化。</span></span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span leaf=\"\">从模拟到现实的跨越</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后一步，是把模拟环境中训练好的策略应用到真实的机器人上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模拟机器人只是高维机电系统的近似，在模拟环境中训练的策略只能保证在这些模拟机器人上有效，不一定能在真实机器人上正常工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04f320ff-6ed2-44e6-f31e-1e468afff000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505095912\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04f320ff-6ed2-44e6-f31e-1e468afff000/public\"></span><span style=\"display: none;line-height: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">‍</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为解决这个问题，在模拟训练时，采用域随机化技术，随机改变每个机器人的物理属性，让策略能适应各种不同的情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这有助于策略零样本泛化到真实机器人上，而无需任何额外的微调。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，在真实机器人上，用千赫兹速率扭矩反馈控制，来修正执行器模型的误差。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样，即使机器人之间有些差异，如地面摩擦力不同，或受到外界推搡，这个策略都具有鲁棒性，能让Figure 02机器人像人一样行走。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，10个Figure 02机器人用得都是同一个RL神经网络。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f1a8a33-892c-4021-fdbd-4b83967bb100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505095913\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f1a8a33-892c-4021-fdbd-4b83967bb100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">说明现有的策略不用再做调整，就能推广到大批机器人，对未来的大规模商业应用是个好消息。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span leaf=\"\">Fi</span><span style=\"display: none;line-height: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">‍</span></span><span leaf=\"\">gure Robotics</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"></span></h2>\n  <section style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f61d25fa-c943-4b05-628e-b3416de66e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.537962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"2734\" data-height=\"1472\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"303\" data-imgfileid=\"505095906\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f61d25fa-c943-4b05-628e-b3416de66e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Figure Robotics是一家新兴的机器人公司，专注于开发通用人形机器人，旨在通过先进的人工智能扩展人类能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">公司专注于构建像人类一样学习和推理的机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Figure Robotics一开始与OpenAI合作，然而在内部人工智能（Helix）方面取得「重大突破」后，于2025年2月结束了合作，Figure Robotics转为自主开发Helix VLA模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Figure 02具有肉眼看起来最接近未来成熟形态的外形设计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简直和威尔史密斯《I,Robot》中的机器人如出一辙，浑圆的面罩模型也避免了恐怖谷效应。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b4fc8031-4c96-4768-799f-b0f2b813fc00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;height: auto !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;\" data-width=\"1306\" data-height=\"732\" data-imgfileid=\"505095905\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b4fc8031-4c96-4768-799f-b0f2b813fc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">身高和体重也完美模拟一个成年男性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当机器人能像人类一样学会自然行走，是否意味着也能像人一样学会其他「自然」动作？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更加重要的一个「隐喻」是，目前所有的人形机器人都是按照人类的形态打造的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这更加方便了未来机器人与人类生活的融合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了自然行走，机器人还有很多「人类技能」需要学习，但他们已经在路上了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/Figure_robot/status/1904534311589785885</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.figure.ai/news/reinforcement-learning-walking</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/923736da-3982-4b1d-5907-a29651e1fe00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7472222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"505095904\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/923736da-3982-4b1d-5907-a29651e1fe00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0e40072-bb22-49bd-506d-6cb16ced2b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.1540880503144654\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"636\" style=\"outline: 0px;display: initial;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 367px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095903\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0e40072-bb22-49bd-506d-6cb16ced2b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Figure Robotics 利用强化学习和物理模拟，成功训练机器人像人一样自然行走，并实现策略在多个机器人间的零样本迁移。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Figure Robotics 利用强化学习和物理模拟，成功训练机器人像人一样自然行走，并实现策略在多个机器人间的零样本迁移。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 Figure 公司在人形机器人控制方面的新进展。他们使用强化学习在纯模拟环境中训练 Figure 02 机器人行走，通过高保真物理模拟器在短时间内生成大量训练数据。为了解决模拟环境与真实环境的差异，采用了域随机化和高频扭矩反馈等技术，成功将模拟环境中训练的策略零样本迁移到真实机器人上。这意味着一个神经网络策略可以控制多个机器人，无需额外调整。此外，文章还简要介绍了 Figure Robotics 公司的背景，包括其与 OpenAI 的合作以及自主研发 Helix VLA 模型，以及人形机器人与人类生活融合的未来前景。",
